org.tagaprice.client.gwt.client.generics
Class TokenCreator

java.lang.Object
  org.tagaprice.client.gwt.client.generics.TokenCreator

public class TokenCreator
extends java.lang.Object

The TokenCreator is able implode and explode a token. You should use the TokenCreator when you create a token or you wanna split a token. With the TokenCreator it is very easy and secure, when you work with your own tokens.
